      • ALL_PUBLIC

        public static final java.util.Set<java.lang.String> ALL_PUBLIC
        constant containing the set of all public field names

      • document

        public MidataId document
        the id of the document record this record belongs to. This field is null for all records that are not part of a document This field is not encrypted but stored in the database.

      • stream

        public MidataId stream

      • part

        public java.lang.String part
        a part name for records that are part of a document, This field is null for all records that are not part of a document This field is not encrypted but stored in the database

      • id

        public java.lang.String id
        an alternative ID for this record that has the access permission set ID also encoded in the ID. This field is computed upon request and is neither stored in the database nor contained in the encrypted part

      • version

        public java.lang.String version
        version of this document

      • owner

        public MidataId owner
        the id of the owner of this record. The owner is the person the data of this record belongs to. This field is neither stored in the database nor contained in the encrypted part of the record. The owner information is derived from information of the APS this record is stored in or from the owner of the stream this record is stored in.

      • ownerName

        public java.lang.String ownerName
        firstname lastname of the owner of this record. This field is neither stored in the database nor contained in the encrypted part of the record. This field is computed upon request from the owner field

      • creatorName

        public java.lang.String creatorName
        firstname lastname of the creator of this record This field is neither stored in the database nor contained in the encrypted part of the record. This field is computed upon request from the creator field

      • format

        public java.lang.String format
        The format of the records data. This is the syntactical data format. This field is contained in the encrypted part of the record.

      • content

        public java.lang.String content
        The content type of the records data. This is the semantical data format. This field is contained in the encrypted part of the record.

      • code

        public java.util.Set<java.lang.String> code
        The content system+code of the records data. This is the semantical data format expressed as a code system + code pair. This field is contained in the encrypted part of the record.

      • group

        public java.lang.String group
        The group name where the record will be placed in the record tree This field is neither stored in the database nor contained in the encrypted part of the record.

      • isStream

        public boolean isStream
        Is this record a stream record? This field is neither stored in the database nor contained in the encrypted part of the record. This field is only internally used.

      • app

        public MidataId app
        the id of the plugin that created this record The contents of this field is stored in the encrypted part of this record

      • creator

        public MidataId creator
        the id of the user that created this record The contents of this field is stored in the encrypted part of this record. If the creator is the same as the owner the creator is not stored

      • created

        public java.util.Date created
        record creation timestamp The contents of this field is stored in the encrypted part of this record

      • lastUpdated

      • tags

      • data
